  <brief_title>Study of Exelon Transdermal Patch in Amnestic Mild Cognitive Impairment Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>24-week, Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled, Parallel Group Study of the Exelon® [Rivastigmine] Transdermal Patch in 120 APOE e4 Positive Amnestic MCI Patients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
